Open the SML interpreter and type in
						
						use "Path/To/Polynomial.sml";

to import the functions used in this file.

Functions to be used:   addPoly(string, string) => string for addition
						subPoly(string, string) => string for subtraction
						mulPoly(string, string) => string for multiplication
						divPoly(string, string) => string for division
						powPoly(string, int)    => string for power
						integratePoly(string)   => string for integration
						factorizePoly(string)   => string for factorization

Extent of Factorization:
	The algorithm used is capable of handling factorizations of polynomials with integral coefficients. It is capable of completely factorising polynomials with at most one irreducible quadrartic factor
